{"tid":1015361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神] 19歲全裸拍《同班同學》郭奕芯獲邵音音大讚有潛質","createTime":"2019-02-10T02:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T14:41:07.000Z","uid":12558,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"465484a2dde39e7f592061f1c94221fefe8412f1","tid":1015361,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"賀歲片《恭喜八婆》的演員陣容都是彭浩翔的固定班底，包括《低俗喜劇》陳靜、《香港仔》梁詠琪、《伊莎貝拉》梁洛施、《志明與春嬌》楊千嬅、林兆霞及郭奕芯等。<br />\n說起郭奕芯，未必人人認識，她於19歲時已擔正演出由彭浩翔監製、女導演陸以心首次執導的《同班同學》。電影還成功衝出國際，入圍東京國際電影節及台灣金馬獎最佳亞洲電影，雖然最後與獎項擦身而過，但郭奕芯的大膽演出，成功令觀眾留下印象。<br />\n<br />\n女團Angel girl一員　獲周杰倫、方文山力挺<br />\n<br />\n現年23歲的郭奕芯，一早已有心鋪路入行，<span style=\"color: red;\">2009年只有13歲的她，參加由《Yes!》舉辦的全港校花校草選舉，並勇奪「全港甜美校花」大獎。</span>3年後，郭奕芯毅然去北京進修，並獲邀加入華人女團Angel girl。當時Angel Girl在北京舉行出道發布會，首張迷你專輯《花木蘭》由內地著名音樂人許嵩和台灣著名填詞人方文山聯手打造，發布會當日更獲天王周杰倫拍片力挺。<br />\n<br />\n19歲全裸演出《同班同學》<br />\n<br />\n可惜Angel girl很快便消失娛樂圈，之後郭奕芯改以個人發展，在2015年客串演出《壹獄壹世界：高登闊少踎監日記》，同年更初嘗女主角滋味，與廖子妤及麥芷誼合演《同班同學》。電影當時口碑不俗，不少影迷、特別是女影迷大讚電影非常有共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n當中有一幕講述，「林婉靜」郭奕芯被「婆婆」邵音音懷疑學壞紋身，命令她除衫檢查。而「婆婆」邵音音沒有留手，真打郭奕芯。事後慘被「藤條炆豬肉」的她獲音音姐大讚「她好有潛質」。<br />\n<br />\n獲夏雨欽點做《鬼網》女主角<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2017年，郭奕芯再獲夏雨垂青，力邀她成為電影《鬼網》其中一個故事《好鄰居》的女主角</span>，其他演員包括陳家樂、簡淑兒及張建聲等人。當時夏雨曾透露郭奕芯試鏡表現出色，還為拍好電影而去學樂器ukuleleh。她認真就是被選上的原因。<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次郭奕芯在《恭喜八婆》的演出是客串形式，但不乏搶鏡畫面，尤其她擁有突出身材，足以與性感女神陳靜（Dada）一較高下，未來或許有機會成為Dada接班人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RzZ9Kc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RzZ9Kc.png&h=b505e47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xx5KBpc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXx5KBpc.png&h=91edaa2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALKn7vU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALKn7vU.png&h=84a1f26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOCw0QU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOCw0QU.png&h=92f1c3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pu4fH4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpu4fH4f.png&h=22edeea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eba48cc8431a280ab9ee8b2928ee36c57327822","tid":1015361,"uid":31611,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"以前叫小蕉 而家整到完全另一個樣"},{"pid":"15e7222bb1d1ce132aead168ca3f61752bdb2c8d","tid":1015361,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"條鼻樑闊過西隧 咩料"},{"pid":"b21975747a00ca4e0065e2336e7ab7764ee787db","tid":1015361,"uid":57504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"雞味"},{"pid":"7c764f0ffaaa5f4426f9155831a63d2ced7bc432","tid":1015361,"uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b21975747a00ca4e0065e2336e7ab7764ee787db","tid":1015361,"uid":57504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"雞味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"同班同學果期幾好J<br />\n乖乖女開左曉後 王宗堯都降唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a284a2bba7a2da143123cf631934019a2a40b83","tid":1015361,"uid":200328,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://driver.cool3c.com/files/10/contentparty/7f7bdc7c-e815-4f96-a495-d2938102cff0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdriver.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2F10%2Fcontentparty%2F7f7bdc7c-e815-4f96-a495-d2938102cff0.png&h=d2cf6a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1242f82767aaba1f964add2a13b766735f68fd04","tid":1015361,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gftj9Vy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgftj9Vy.png&h=dca3f32e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2aOiOU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2aOiOU.png&h=7e1db088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKkKBAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKkKBAB.png&h=0cbf726f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/es5q5tZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fes5q5tZ.png&h=7336b544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQ6UYO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQ6UYO1.png&h=11227af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaerPVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaerPVJ.png&h=e379e3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nAbgAK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nAbgAK.png&h=f4edd34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYKCWAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYKCWAM.png&h=cce7fc03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a47615dd834e421e44e3e57f2ea888b04c69176","tid":1015361,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c364c83c333efe1144ef3c50736a175fddfb344","tid":1015361,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"Cammi遭拖累不屑認朋友<br />\nAshina承認整容<br />\n<br />\n盛品儒早前被有米女友蔡一鳳狠撇，他上周即偷嗒有翻版謝安琪之稱的𡃁模郭奕芯（Ashina）療情傷，兩人啜爆街頭，盛品儒其後發現有人借緋聞催谷寫真，有意搵舊愛蔡一鳳箍煲，據知兩人掟煲唔掟蓋，仍有聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n零知名度C奶Ashina，火速借緋聞上位，她今年書展更推出倒奶寫真。昨日有讀者報料，大爆Ashina和𡃁模謝芷蕙（Cammi）是「整容雙嬌」，從兩女的舊照看來，她們現在樣貌跟從前變化很大。Ashina五官默默起革命，她在14歲時以舊名郭嘉銘（小蕉）參加「Yes!!全港校花校草選舉2009」，當時的拉票宣傳片中，她仍是方臉、扁鼻兼平胸，可是現在拍寫真卻有一對大眼、間尺鼻、V煞臉，以及C奶導彈，變化非常明顯。<br />\n鼻同下巴整過<br />\n有指Ashina整容後又改名郭思嵐（Gabby），似乎想借新名字掩飾過去。Ashina被揭改頭換臉，記者昨日致電求證，她直認去年整容：「我貪靚，鼻同下巴打過針，我想鼻高啲，下巴尖啲，眼同個胸係真嘅。」Ashina認為整容後自信心增加：「我心理上比以前好，不過適可而止，身體其他部位都唔會整，唯一只想減肥。我認得整容，唔介意人哋眼光，我控制唔到。」<br />\n<br />\nAshina的整容新聞卻連累Cammi被翻舊賬，Cammi昨在電話中劃清界線：「佢係我中學同學嘅朋友，好耐冇聯絡。」可覺Ashina整過容？Cammi揶揄：「係女仔都女大十八變，變得越嚟越靚係好事。」會撐Ashina買她的寫真嗎？Cammi不屑：「同佢唔算朋友，佢唔係我值得欣賞嘅人，我係唔會買。」<br />\n此外，Cammi真面目又再曝光，Cammi說：「可唔可以唔登嗰啲相？」是不是不滿被Ashina拖累？Cammi無奈說：「我都認咗曾割雙眼皮，同埋打過透明質酸，但𠵱家都溶解咗，網民係鍾意翻舊賬，我承認以前整容係細個無知，𠵱家好後悔。」<br />\n採訪：楊定"},{"pid":"2177104a015a7f9deccf98fcad3e44af4272dd03","tid":1015361,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"化左妝都咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f4f47da539314d71dee3acc24c8af5ca3f6745","tid":1015361,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c364c83c333efe1144ef3c50736a175fddfb344","tid":1015361,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"Cammi遭拖累不屑認朋友<br />\nAshina承認整容<br />\n<br />\n盛品儒早前被有米女友蔡一鳳狠撇，他上周即偷嗒有翻版謝安琪之稱的𡃁模郭奕芯（Ashina）療情傷，兩人啜爆街頭，盛品儒其後發現有人借緋聞催谷寫真，有意搵舊愛蔡一鳳箍煲，據知兩人掟煲唔掟蓋，仍有聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n零知名度C奶Ashina，火速借緋聞上位，她今年書展更推出倒奶寫真。昨日有讀者報料，大爆Ashina和𡃁模謝芷蕙（Cammi）是「整容雙嬌」，從兩女的舊照看來，她們現在樣貌跟從前變化很大。Ashina五官默默起革命，她在14歲時以舊名郭嘉銘（小蕉）參加「Yes!!全港校花校草選舉2009」，當時的拉票宣傳片中，她仍是方臉、扁鼻兼平胸，可是現在拍寫真卻有一對大眼、間尺鼻、V煞臉，以及C奶導彈，變化非常明顯。<br />\n鼻同下巴整過<br />\n有指Ashina整容後又改名郭思嵐（Gabby），似乎想借新名字掩飾過去。Ashina被揭改頭換臉，記者昨日致電求證，她直認去年整容：「我貪靚，鼻同下巴打過針，我想鼻高啲，下巴尖啲，眼同個胸係真嘅。」Ashina認為整容後自信心增加：「我心理上比以前好，不過適可而止，身體其他部位都唔會整，唯一只想減肥。我認得整容，唔介意人哋眼光，我控制唔到。」<br />\n<br />\nAshina的整容新聞卻連累Cammi被翻舊賬，Cammi昨在電話中劃清界線：「佢係我中學同學嘅朋友，好耐冇聯絡。」可覺Ashina整過容？Cammi揶揄：「係女仔都女大十八變，變得越嚟越靚係好事。」會撐Ashina買她的寫真嗎？Cammi不屑：「同佢唔算朋友，佢唔係我值得欣賞嘅人，我係唔會買。」<br />\n此外，Cammi真面目又再曝光，Cammi說：「可唔可以唔登嗰啲相？」是不是不滿被Ashina拖累？Cammi無奈說：「我都認咗曾割雙眼皮，同埋打過透明質酸，但𠵱家都溶解咗，網民係鍾意翻舊賬，我承認以前整容係細個無知，𠵱家好後悔。」<br />\n採訪：楊定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"依家其實個個都有𢴇個架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290ccf3491908d196b973272c7af72a722e9995d","tid":1015361,